 (4712, 1, '2015-06-23 19:26:58', '2015-06-23 11:26:58', '<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to subscribe our calendar to your Google Calendar</h2>\r\n<a href="javascript:history.back()"><img class=" size-full wp-image-4731 imgborder alignnone" src="http://www.astro.ncu.edu.tw/~yhsu/OhBearTaiwan/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/btn_back.png" alt="btn_back" /></a>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">步驟一：</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">登入自己的Google日曆後，點擊"其他日曆"中的"輸入網址以新增"。</p>\r\n<img class=" size-full wp-image-4662 imgborder aligncenter" src="http://www.astro.ncu.edu.tw/~yhsu/OhBearTaiwan/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/ohbear-ical-zh.png" alt="ohbear-ical-zh" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">步驟二：</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">在"輸入網址以新增"的彈出視窗中輸入網址<span style="color: #ff0000;">『http://www.astro.ncu.edu.tw/~yhsu/OhBearTaiwan/en/events.ics』</span>，點擊"新增日曆"後即完成訂閱。</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"> <img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-4681 imgborder" src="http://www.astro.ncu.edu.tw/~yhsu/OhBearTaiwan/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/ohbear-ical-zh2.png" alt="ohbear-ical-zh2" /></p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<a href="javascript:history.back()"><img class=" size-full wp-image-4731 imgborder alignleft" src="http://www.astro.ncu.edu.tw/~yhsu/OhBearTaiwan/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/btn_back.png" alt="btn_back" /></a>', '訂閱活動', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'icalfeeds', '', '', '2015-06-26 23:05:48', '2015-06-26 15:05:48', '', 0, 'http://www.astro.ncu.edu.tw/~yhsu/OhBearTaiwan/icalfeeds-2/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
